# Type 1 Example of Listed Items

public class Mean_type_1 {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		
		 int sum = 0;
	     int mean = 0;
	    int a[]={222,236,242,242,236,238,230,248,249,247};  
	    
	 int count = a.length;
	   
	    for(int i=0;i<a.length;i++){
	    
	    sum = sum + a[i];
	   
	    }
	   System.out.println("The total sum of all wages are : "+sum);
	    System.out.println("The total no of elements in the array are : "+count);
	   
	   mean  = sum / count;
	   System.out.println("and the mean value of these wages is : "+mean+" Units");
	}

}
----------------------------
Output is : 
The total sum of all wages are : 2390
The total no of elements in the array are : 10
and the mean value of these wages is : 239 Units

